'' Relationship Matrix View (GridView)
'' Salt matrix showing pairwise relationships between elements. Cells indicate composite (C), typing (T), specialization (G), and shared (S).
@startuml

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

title Relationship Matrix View

salt
{
| ? | <&question> Engine | <&question> power | <&question> torque | <&question> Vehicle | <&question> engine | <&question> frontLeft | <&question> frontRight | <&question> Wheel
| Engine |  | C | C | S |  |  |  | S
| power |  |  | S |  |  |  |  | 
| torque |  | S |  |  |  |  |  | 
| Vehicle | S |  |  |  | C | C | C | S
| engine |  |  |  |  |  | S | S | 
| frontLeft |  |  |  |  | S |  | S | 
| frontRight |  |  |  |  | S | S |  | 
| Wheel | S |  |  | S |  |  |  | 
}

legend bottom
  <b>Relationship Legend</b>
  C = composite
  S = shared
  T = typing
  G = specialization
  R = redefinition
  B = binding
  N = connector
  F = flow
  U = succession
  A = allocation
  D = dependency
  I = import
endlegend

@enduml